---
// Hero.astro — eyebrow + headline + subhead.
---
<section class="px-6 pt-24 pb-24 text-center sm:px-10">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[900px]">
    <div class="mb-[26px] font-mono text-[12.5px] tracking-[0.14em] text-accent">arrca · RCA FOR KUBERNETES</div>
    <h1 class="mx-auto mb-5 max-w-[760px] text-[clamp(30px,5vw,42px)] font-semibold leading-[1.18] tracking-[-0.025em] text-ink-900">
      A continuously-updated topology of your Kubernetes estate built from the k8s API and OTel metrics and traces.
    </h1>
    <p class="mx-auto max-w-[600px] text-[18px] leading-[1.6] text-ink-600">
      Install the arrca Helm chart and point your otel-collector at it. Zero setup overhead.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
